title: Bonus Podcast With Brooke Castillo
itunes:title: Bonus Podcast With Brooke Castillo
description: Kara and Brooke Castillo of the Life Coach School explore how the Covid-19 outbreak is presenting a unique opportunity for us to level up our thought work skills. Learn why loneliness, fear, and misery are not inevitable reactions to the crisis - and how to shift your thinking to get relief.
